data.description: This spacious home offers something for everyone! From the grand two-story foyer to the beautiful hardwood floors, you'll be feeling at home as soon as you walk through the door! The large kitchen, overlooking a cozy family room, is perfect for entertaining. Outside, an awesome stone patio awaits, ideal for cookouts or just relaxing in the sunshine. Upstairs, the oversized master bedroom boasts a large walk-in closet and his and hers vanities in the bathroom. Conveniently, the laundry room is located upstairs near the master bedroom. Additionally, there's a formal living room, perfect for guests or as an office space, and a formal dining room adjacent to the kitchen, ready to host all your loved ones. Situated on a corner lot with a side-entry garage and level driveway, this home is the epitome of comfort and convenience.
